ote><br />\n<br />\n知"},{"pid":"c58866e753c5496b7dfe7e9760c501e0cda934e7","tid":321123,"uid":110268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:31:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>視乎你本身成績點樣<br />\n<br />\nelectives 黎講, 最好暑假清晒concepts, 成績好既可以開始操多D paper/exercise, 成績冇咁好既就主要重溫concepts.<br />\n<br />\ncore就一定要keep住浸淫下, 唔好耐唔耐先睇幾下, 暑假開始浸既話, 底子幾差都可以上到4左右, 好既自然更上層樓.<br />\n<br />\n深入D既就想合再講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成績ok 係數差D<br />\n巴打你建唔建議去補數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係自己溫書操pp"},{"pid":"22a2027a13e60c5132cc7a821be088aaa0cbacc1","tid":321123,"uid":27196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:54:52.000Z","msg":"你假設自己係dse成績係點？"},{"pid":"df064e4681c8e37d952aded804321a3b083e8f1a","tid":321123,"uid":66460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:58:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>視乎你本身成績點樣<br />\n<br />\nelectives 黎講, 最好暑假清晒concepts, 成績好既可以開始操多D paper/exercise, 成績冇咁好既就主要重溫concepts.<br />\n<br />\ncore就一定要keep住浸淫下, 唔好耐唔耐先睇幾下, 暑假開始浸既話, 底子幾差都可以上到4左右, 好既自然更上層樓.<br />\n<br />\n深入D既就想合再講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成績ok 係數差D<br />\n巴打你建唔建議去補數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係自己溫書操pp</blockquote><br />\n數差可以考慮私補<br />\n自己溫既話 睇你有無悟性"},{"pid":"72411e27cad349ab9aa1d6295940b8fca84d2ece","tid":321123,"uid":71708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T06:04:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>視乎你本身成績點樣<br />\n<br />\nelectives 黎講, 最好暑假清晒concepts, 成績好既可以開始操多D paper/exercise, 成績冇咁好既就主要重溫concepts.<br />\n<br />\ncore就一定要keep住浸淫下, 唔好耐唔耐先睇幾下, 暑假開始浸既話, 底子幾差都可以上到4左右, 好既自然更上層樓.<br />\n<br />\n深入D既就想合再講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成績ok 係數差D<br />\n巴打你建唔建議去補數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係自己溫書操pp</blockquote><br />\n數差可以考慮私補<br />\n自己溫既話 睇你有無悟性</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意, 數底好既睇下examples已經明晒嗰個chapters既做法同埋應用, 冇謂花錢補<br />\n數底麻麻既話, 自己溫就會好晒時間, 不如花少少錢搵人講解下"},{"pid":"52a8a1d2f3a334736f1b39ff1a475f8bd5025ffb","tid":321123,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:53:27.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"67dc9a2f6bab4efa7bcc78ce6b05861d42b3bb2f","tid":321123,"uid":91723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:07:00.000Z","msg":"我個時係幾乎日日摺自修室<br />\n但成效唔大，發夢多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住日日溫10粒鐘，最後6-7粒鐘都已達極限，多數2-3粒鐘收檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係叫做堅持到日日摺係個溫書環境到<br />\n所以我覺得第一件事set個合理target比自己先<br />\n如果唔係chur開嘅人，暑假一開始日日溫2-3粒鐘先，再慢慢加上去<br />\n<br />\n然後每日去自修室（或者係你嘅溫書地方）都要有planning<br />\n同意樓上巴打講core要浸，electives可靠短期操（如果concept夠清的話）<br />\n最好每朝都整篇中or eng p123 mock/文言文練習/睇下中or英新聞先<br />\n晏就就睇你係邊類人<br />\n1. 想連續溫幾日同一科<br />\n2. 想梅花間竹咁溫唔同科<br />\n我個人覺得1係好啲嘅<br />\n我自己多數係用3-4日溫同一科<br />\n<br />\n整個calendar寫明邊日溫邊科，溫幾耐，溫完寫低完唔完成到當日tagret"},{"pid":"972eb413dea88ce8559b8559482eb0ca3de66e61","tid":321123,"uid":33390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:11:04.000Z","msg":"同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己core除咗數都唔錯但係啲electives就兩年都冇上過堂咁濟依家要死追<br />\n自己暫時有睇下書想中英文穩陣啲但都驚咁落去溫唔翻切bio econ同數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa556300cf45164ac8ae83d24864e487170da28b","tid":321123,"uid":110268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T01:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我個時係幾乎日日摺自修室<br />\n但成效唔大，發夢多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住日日溫10粒鐘，最後6-7粒鐘都已達極限，多數2-3粒鐘收檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係叫做堅持到日日摺係個溫書環境到<br />\n所以我覺得第一件事set個合理target比自己先<br />\n如果唔係chur開嘅人，暑假一開始日日溫2-3粒鐘先，再慢慢加上去<br />\n<br />\n然後每日去自修室（或者係你嘅溫書地方）都要有planning<br />\n同意樓上巴打講core要浸，electives可靠短期操（如果concept夠清的話）<br />\n最好每朝都整篇中or eng p123 mock/文言文練習/睇下中or英新聞先<br />\n晏就就睇你係邊類人<br />\n1. 想連續溫幾日同一科<br />\n2. 想梅花間竹咁溫唔同科<br />\n我個人覺得1係好啲嘅<br />\n我自己多數係用3-4日溫同一科<br />\n<br />\n整個calendar寫明邊日溫邊科，溫幾耐，溫完寫低完唔完成到當日tagret</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n爸打最後幾分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecfd2d44a65512d210964f2816971bf259c34bb","tid":321123,"uid":110268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T01:45:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己core除咗數都唔錯但係啲electives就兩年都冇上過堂咁濟依家要死追<br />\n自己暫時有睇下書想中英文穩陣啲但都驚咁落去溫唔翻切bio econ同數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18f1a2ac83e8218d5c9450c837b5173c63e9f85","tid":321123,"uid":69140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T01:56:25.000Z","msg":"我667 phy chem econ<br />\n唔算好勁但都有少少心得<br />\n先講maths 同 electives<br />\n最好温筆記後即做pp <br />\nPp 要 by topic 唔好 咁快做by year <br />\n而econ 年年係最遲考 <br />\nDse期間有十七日温<br />\n所以我study leave focus phy chem only (時間一定唔夠要有取捨)<br />\n做哂pp  + 知錯能改 一定有lv 5 or above<br />\n而暑假要多温中英LS<br />\n好多嘢要記要背<br />\n早啲背係會唔記得 但係再睇多一兩次就會上翻腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好忽視每一份分卷<br />\n我以為中文作文同speaking 有5**點知得4 好彩綜合5**拉翻overall 5*<br />\nYou never know <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打仲有時間好好俾心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792a57eb4aa3b44874711ef53eec4856be8ccecb","tid":321123,"uid":69140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T01:58:40.000Z","msg":"有一點好重要:<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定係做past paper 先<br />\n好多理科坊間exercise係大伏 錯concept out-syl 咩都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"3ac31cf3c7e8d60e00f55e0a25dabec2239ad97c","tid":321123,"uid":2904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T02:38:42.000Z","msg":"個人認為通識學答題技巧就得<br />\n如果你平時做卷都吹到兩咀 成績唔差<br />\n有留意下新聞<br />\n我建議可以放少啲時間落通識<br />\n我好多fd都係符出同收入唔成正比<br />\n我就冇乜點溫 最後lv5<br />\n但如果你想入果科通識有高weighting就另計"},{"pid":"506ae73f70f802a0ada4103f554f6d262f4caec3","tid":321123,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T02:45:39.000Z","msg":"當年中五升中六暑假，唔計星期六日紅日淨係放左3日假，其餘全部要返學補課，補課除左教書會做exercise同PP，同每日intensively溫2+個鐘書無分別<br />\n最後間學校入三大、八大率都好高（不過教出黎既人就好薯...）<br />\n加油，搏盡"},{"pid":"332492d3f67bf493af5f3c22f3c67f1eac8077fa","tid":321123,"uid":91723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T02:45:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我個時係幾乎日日摺自修室<br />\n但成效唔大，發夢多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住日日溫10粒鐘，最後6-7粒鐘都已達極限，多數2-3粒鐘收檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係叫做堅持到日日摺係個溫書環境到<br />\n所以我覺得第一件事set個合理target比自己先<br />\n如果唔係chur開嘅人，暑假一開始日日溫2-3粒鐘先，再慢慢加上去<br />\n<br />\n然後每日去自修室（或者係你嘅溫書地方）都要有planning<br />\n同意樓上巴打講core要浸，electives可靠短期操（如果concept夠清的話）<br />\n最好每朝都整篇中or eng p123 mock/文言文練習/睇下中or英新聞先<br />\n晏就就睇你係邊類人<br />\n1. 想連續溫幾日同一科<br />\n2. 想梅花間竹咁溫唔同科<br />\n我個人覺得1係好啲嘅<br />\n我自己多數係用3-4日溫同一科<br />\n<br />\n整個calendar寫明邊日溫邊科，溫幾耐，溫完寫低完唔完成到當日tagret</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n爸打最後幾分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廿尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d4437687013d792dd0c061c0fb65737ff88422","tid":321123,"uid":63152,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:01:34.000Z","msg":"唔洗哂咁多時間溫中通 溫黎都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64dc74a45cbe844f3a86bbee38ed76b6d78c10b0","tid":321123,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:11:38.000Z","msg":"Hist由07ce dbq做起<br />\nEssay就dse開始做<br />\n利申 2017得5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b167026e1f9d715af585ab654a48f4e16b0c0846","tid":321123,"uid":3066,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:12:56.000Z","msg":"建議你每日去hku圖書館溫書<br />\n因為每個人aim既野唔同<br />\n但非hku學生去hku溫書就一定有motivation"},{"pid":"ac8548dc9ac9bf5a6e3974a90f006f2bb9feb73f","tid":321123,"uid":35894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:18:54.000Z","msg":"巴打你數學大概aim咩分？<br />\n數學最緊要就keep住操唔好生疏<br />\n發覺邊題唔明記得問 再做到明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e023bb4ce54f3bdc3cfc2a6b49ff9ca28f2e1c","tid":321123,"uid":6407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:19:57.000Z","msg":"去hku 24hr房溫書"}]}